So, you know what
you're gonna wish for?

20:24.200 --> 20:26.200
What are you doing here, Byrd?

20:26.200 --> 20:29.900
- Lose your compass on your migration?
- She's back.

20:30.333 --> 20:33.067
If you don't mind, I'm trying to
have a private conversation here.

20:34.400 --> 20:36.333
- Oh, sure.
- [ Huffs ]

20:41.600 --> 20:43.600
